course.subject: MGMT
course.name: New Venture Business Development
course.description: This course will introduce students to the new emerged thinking and methodologies on entrepreneurship and venture business development which enhance the chance of success and to reduce time and costs of failure in new ventures. Topics will cover major stages of new venture business development, ranging from ideation, searching for problem-solution fit, building business to achieve product-market fit, and scaling business. Graded P or F.
